        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A five-minute tapping practice from Day 59 of a 12-week money program. The script targets the contraction pattern around spending: money leaving feels like loss, the balance dropping reads as bad news, every payment carries a slight dread. The reframe moves toward money in motion as the active evidence of a circulating system, money that moves and comes back.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to tapping? Read ",
